  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery Digger: Definitive Edition - short and relaxing mining simulator where you control a drilling machine stuck in a strange tunnel. Dig deeper, upgrade your equipment, and overcome obstacles, you’ll discover hidden notes and mysterious artifacts that gradually reveal the story of this place. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No rush. No pressure. Just the tunnel, your machine, and the mystery waiting at the end. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dig</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/a403228175d9d0a791359bcf8163be35.poster.avif?t=1773775842\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/a403228175d9d0a791359bcf8163be35.webm?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/a403228175d9d0a791359bcf8163be35.mp4?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/c746555858dfa35d3542c0c78528d420.poster.avif?t=1773775842\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/c746555858dfa35d3542c0c78528d420.webm?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/c746555858dfa35d3542c0c78528d420.mp4?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/089b5d00681046f97dd15d65c2bfa362.poster.avif?t=1773775842\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/089b5d00681046f97dd15d65c2bfa362.webm?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/089b5d00681046f97dd15d65c2bfa362.mp4?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/1308b5bc8d9f36aa234dda0a4840d51b.poster.avif?t=1773775842\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/1308b5bc8d9f36aa234dda0a4840d51b.webm?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4255250/extras/1308b5bc8d9f36aa234dda0a4840d51b.mp4?t=1773775842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn money by mining valuable resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your drilling machine to reach deeper levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover strange artifacts and hidden notes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a calm and atmospheric experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls and pixel art graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short experience — usually completed in a couple of evenings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery Digger: Definitive Edition is an enhanced and expanded Steam version of <i>Mystery Digger</i>.</p>",
