      "playtime_at_review": 28,
      "review_text": "This game gets boring pretty quickly. Progress is painfully slow, and you can’t even let it run in the background to earn money because fuel runs out every 30 seconds or so, forcing you to constantly refill it. On top of that, your machine breaks down every 10 seconds after, so you’re stuck repairing it all the time.\n\nAs if that wasn’t enough, random “monsters” show up and interrupt you. Some of them are extremely tanky, especially if you don’t have the right bullets. If you’ve spent your gems on different ammo, be prepared to spend several minutes just trying to take one down.",
      "timestamp_created": 1773830630
    }
  ]
